                    <introduction>

<assemblage>
  <title>Motivating Questions</title>
  <p>
  <statement>
	Here are some questions we'll consider.
	<ol>
	  <li>How can struggle be productive?</li>
	  <li>What role does mathematics play in helping us discern truth?</li>
	  <li>How can we establish identities by counting in two different ways?</li>
	</ol>
